14/10/2003
ATHENS, Greece -- US Secretary of State Colin Powell will arrive in Athens on 22 October to meet with Greek Foreign Minister George Papandreou and his Turkish counterpart, Abdullah Gul. The focus will be on Greek-Turkish relations.
In other news, Greek President Costis Stephanopoulos left on Tuesday (14 October) for a three-day official visit to Serbia-Montenegro. (MPA, ANA - 13/10/03)
